Package org.hibernate.boot.model.domain

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BasicValueMapping<J>
    A ValueMapping extension for basic-valued mappings
    BasicValueMapping.Resolution<J>
    Resolved form of BasicValueMapping as part of interpreting the boot-time model into the run-time model
    EmbeddableJavaTypeMapping<T>  
    EmbeddedValueMapping
    Models an embeddable-valued mapping such as an Embedded or a ElementCollection
    EntityJavaTypeMapping<T>
    Contract for java type mappings of "entities".
    EntityMapping  
    EntityMappingHierarchy  
    IdentifiableJavaTypeMapping<T>
    Contract for identifiable java type mappings, which is taken from the JPA term for commonality between entity and "mapped superclass" types.
    IdentifiableTypeMapping  
    JavaTypeMapping<T>
    Contract which describes the Java side of a mapping that can be later resolved to a JavaTypeDescriptor during the runtime model creation process.
    ManagedJavaTypeMapping<T>
    Contract for "managed types", which is taken from the JPA term for commonality between entity, embeddable, and "mapped superclass" types.
    ManagedTypeMapping
    Corollary to what JPA calls a "managed type" as part of Hibernate's boot-time metamodel.
    MappedJoin
    Common representation of both SecondaryTable and joined-tables from inheritance.
    MappedSuperclassJavaTypeMapping<T>
    Contract for "mapped superclass" java type mappings which is a direct correlary to the JPA term "mapped superclass".
    MappedSuperclassMapping  
    MetaAttributable<T extends MetaAttributeMapping>  
    MetaAttributeMapping
    Common contract for all things that can handle meta attributes.
    PersistentAttributeMapping  
    ResolutionContext  
    ValueMapping<J>
    Corollary to Navigable in the runtime model
    ValueMappingContainer  
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    NotYetResolvedException
    Indicates access to something that is not yet resolved/ready-to-use.
